description: KruCraft project architecture and rules
globs: ["src/**/*", "prisma/**/*", "middleware.ts"]
alwaysApply: true
---

This project is a SaaS learning resource marketplace.

Tech stack:
Next.js 14 App Router
TypeScript
Tailwind
Prisma
PostgreSQL
NextAuth
Stripe
Xendit

Key rules:

- Never break authentication system
- Never expose private uploads
- Always enforce ownership checks on downloads
- Use Prisma transactions for purchase state changes
- Follow existing folder structure
- Never expose private-uploads folder via public routes
- All downloads must go through /api/download authorization
- Never trust client input for file paths
- All payments must be verified via webhook before granting access
